 Task 4: Average Age of Approved Customers 
Find the average age of customers whose claims are Approved. 
------------------------------------------------------------

Code:
# for loop
total_age = 0
approved_count = claim_status.count("Approved")
for i in range(len(customer_age)):
  if claim_status[i] == "Approved":
    total_age += customer_age[i]
avg_age = total_age / approved_count
print(f"Average Age of Approved Claims: {avg_age}")

